					<description><![CDATA[7月新鲜上市的水果太多了，多到写不下介绍 桃子、葡萄、龙眼、蓝莓、杏子都正当季 特别是水蜜桃，成熟的已经是中熟 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b8fe97e04709541f67aad11494dc01f3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">7月新鲜上市的水果太多了，多到写不下介绍</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">桃子、葡萄、龙眼、蓝莓、杏子都正当季</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">特别是水蜜桃，成熟的已经是中熟期很甜的品种了</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">还不快冲</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8211;</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">桃子：</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">中国国家地理标志产品</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">1、阳山水蜜桃-</span><span style="color: green;">江苏省无锡市</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">四大名桃之一</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">7月中旬甜度Z高的湖景蜜露、阳山蜜露上市</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/705b02cd8dccad0d3318965ddccc3625.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/0d6cf2fbb59fc4f1fc447f316cd7dc89.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、奉化水蜜桃-<span style="color: green;">浙江省宁波市</span><span style="color: green;">奉化区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">2000多年历史，四大名桃之一</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/732e567f2776b0e2f10f1cd82c990364.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">3、新沂水蜜桃-江苏省</span><span style="color: green;">新沂市</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：中国沙红、大珍宝、新川中岛、春蜜、春美等</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/925fa96ae872503b03a6c4a2987056c0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">4、南汇水蜜桃-上海市</span><span style="color: green;">南汇区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">前身是上海水蜜桃，多品种</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">5、金山蟠桃-上海市</span><span style="color: green;">金山区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：玉露蟠桃</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/7c5461f0a0788b8417cca81d9a6c04a4.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">以下是全国农产品地理标志</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">穆阳水蜜桃-<span style="color: green;">福建省宁德市</span><span style="color: green;">福安市</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">凤桥水蜜桃-<span style="color: green;">浙江省嘉兴市</span><span style="color: green;">南湖区</span><span style="color: green;">特产，中国桃的原产地之一</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">永乐艳红桃-<span style="color: green;">贵州省贵阳市</span><span style="color: green;">南明区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">&#8211;</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">龙眼：</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">1、茂名储良龙眼</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">广东</span><span style="color: green;">省</span><span style="color: green;">茂名</span><span style="color: green;">市特产，中国国家地理标志产品</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">特点：中等大小，果核小，果肉乳白，爽脆味浓</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/87ea6aa2f13a2b4a06eb3bfd414ab743.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：储良龙眼</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、赤水龙眼-<span style="color: green;">贵州省遵义市赤水市特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">3、平南石硖龙眼-</span><span style="color: green;">广西壮族自治区贵港市平南县</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">4、东璧龙眼-福建省泉州市</span><span style="color: green;">鲤城区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">5、青山龙眼-<span style="color: green;">福建省</span><span style="color: green;">福州市</span><span style="color: green;">长乐区特产，贡品</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/77e3892cb3bcb36b5da003cbd98230b0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">蓝莓：</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">1、中国北极蓝莓</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">黑龙江省</span><span style="color: green;">大兴安岭地区特产，中国国家地理标志产品</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">口感：果肉细腻、口味酸甜</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：笃斯越桔</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/9921d3a3d137d63ba91fd9db3167e18f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、庄河蓝莓-<span style="color: green;">辽宁省大连市庄河市特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：北陆、北村、北蓝、蓝金等</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/7058a123134e2b79d171be17dfe5e7f4.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3、鄂伦春蓝莓 &#8211;<span style="color: green;">内蒙呼伦贝尔市</span><span style="color: green;">鄂伦春自治旗</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">&#8211;</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">葡萄：</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">中国国家地理标志产品</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">1、 吐鲁番葡萄-新疆吐鲁番高昌区特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">特点：多品种，高糖</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：无核白、马奶子、玫瑰红、比夹干、喀什哈尔、黑葡萄、梭梭葡萄等</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/dcb6ecec794be72ea63345917151a922.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">2、张家湾葡萄-北京市</span><span style="color: green;">通州区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：巨峰、京亚、玫瑰香、意大利、里扎马特、矢富罗莎等</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">3、鲁比葡萄-广西壮族自治区柳江区特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">特点：果粉细密，香味纯正，酸甜口</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：巨峰</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1e16e59116a1efafc0fa9c523012dd95.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">4、彭山葡萄-四川省</span><span style="color: green;">眉山市彭山区</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：夏黑、美人指、巨峰、红地球</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">5、海盐葡萄-</span><span style="color: green;">浙江省嘉兴市海盐县</span><span style="color: green;">特产，全国农产品地理标志</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">主栽品种：红地球、醉金香、阳光玫瑰等</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/348e1a9fd6e7f5b3c8f3a8e6d0b684c2.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">&#8211;</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">荔枝：</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">中国国家地理标志产品</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">1、岵山荔枝-福建省永春县特产</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/0d1c132b175fef42ad0657b6677f6f31.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、灵山荔枝-广西壮族自治区灵山县特产</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3、莆田荔枝-福建省莆田市荔城区特产</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">&#8211;</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">其他：</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">中国国家地理标志产品</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">关岭火龙果-<span style="color: green;">贵州省</span><span style="color: green;">安顺市</span><span style="color: green;">关岭布依族苗族自治县特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">罗甸火龙果-贵州省罗甸县特产</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">民勤蜜瓜-甘肃省</span><span style="color: green;">民勤县</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">华坪芒果-<span style="color: green;">云南省丽江市华坪县</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">永德芒果（临沧芒果）-云南省永德县特产</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">沿河沙子空心李-<span style="color: green;">贵州省沿河土家族自治县</span><span style="color: green;">特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">仰韶大杏-</span><span style="color: green;">河南省</span><span style="color: green;">渑池县特产</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">寻乌蜜桔-江西省赣州市寻乌县特产</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">黑水西瓜-吉林省洮南市特产</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/826f2514fcd50a71bc118976f2cf4120.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/da850617c0730ee78c31b95e6ca18051.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
